SubjectOrder Authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force, on behalf of Canada, the Coproduction Agreement in the Areas of Film, Television and On-Demand Audiovisual Media Services between the Government of Canada and the Government of the French Republic
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE, on behalf of Canada, the COPRODUCTION AGREEMENT IN THE AREAS OF FILM, TELEVISION AND ON-DEMAND AUDIOVISUAL MEDIA SERVICES BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE GOVERNMENT OF THE FRENCH REPUBLIC, done at Paris on May 20, 2021, done at Montreal on June 2, 2021 and done at Paris and Montreal on July 28, 2021.
